Use it for free, pay if you get paid. If you make a commercial product with this extension included (e.g. getting paid from a client who wants to have a website made of this product or getting paid from a client who has gotten a website from you made of this product), then I would kindly ask you to give a small donation for about 15 USD to keep this project floating around the world wide web.

Note: If you are from Indonesia and are having problems with the current rupiah exchange rate against the dollar, you are allowed to consider 15 USD as 150,000 IDR.

